{"tid":1234224,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中新社：策動一知半解市民上街　攻擊中央政府","createTime":"2019-06-17T01:12:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-17T18:58:33.000Z","uid":184679,"like":1,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c031097620701d69542edc1e79de971777986a8c","tid":1234224,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:12:54.000Z","msg":"中新社發表評論，認為要以理性對待修例，維護香港法治。<br />\n<br />\n評論表示，不知反對者是反對草案條文內容或修例目的，還是反對立法會二讀等程序，抑或就為了反對修例。在這時候，策動不明就裡、對修例一知半解的普通市民上街，「比拳頭」、「秀肌肉」，似有難言之隱，讓人難免懷疑其背後政治目的，就是摧毀特區政府管治權威，破壞香港與內地關係，攻擊中央政府。<br />\n<br />\n在有些人眼裡，凡事只要香港與內地、與中央政府有關係，就反對，即所謂「逢中必反」。<br />\n<br />\n評論認為，及時修補法律漏洞，更好地預防和打擊犯罪，是香港維護法治核心價值的必然要求，亦是香港避免成為「避罪天堂」的責任，香港社會各界應把握好溝通機遇，更充分、理性討論條例草案，定能求同存異，進而達成更大的共識，共同推動香港法治進步。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463278-20190617.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463278-20190617.htm&d=4IeBTxJtadAFWj01jWWaWv8K46P7%2BXxs1F7ZCKkfkQw%3D&h=17befc48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1463278-20190617.htm&h=1138f234\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1463278-20190617.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a4725690840c9b933a8d4e595dc72419e3c413fe","tid":1234224,"uid":1374,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:15:48.000Z","msg":"佢自己都一知半解遊行目的<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲好意思話遊行既人一知半解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c5f909761eec48a49c8f98e22675e96b3a084c","tid":1234224,"uid":6529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T01:18:26.000Z","msg":"亂寫一通"},{"pid":"8a6f7590d5a552f3821849ee0a1bd0829dace0cf","tid":1234224,"uid":2054,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":